      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's a strong start, definitely captures the energy we're looking for. I like the \"suffocating grip\" line. \n\nCan we lean even harder into the section about the \"progressive elite\"? I want to make it clear that their ideas aren't just different, but that they're actually dangerous and fundamentally incompatible with American life. Maybe something about how their agenda is a direct attack on the moral fabric of the country? Give me another paragraph that hammers that home.",
